事实</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/main-facts-about-copper-market-prices-hit-record-highs-2024-05-20/</link><description>周一，由于空头回补引发的近期反弹，为投机者和基金押注金属价格上涨创造了动力，铜价飙升至历史新高。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 12:55:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/main-facts-about-copper-market-prices-hit-record-highs-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：“Nvidia 周”开局活跃</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-20/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 10:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，中国房价暴跌，今年销售状况将恶化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/slump-chinas-home-prices-sales-set-worsen-this-year-2024-05-20/</link><description>路透调查显示，随着房地产投资和销售下滑​​加剧，今年中国房价将以更快的速度下跌，这对正在加倍努力重振受危机打击的房地产行业的政策制定者来说是一个沉重的提醒。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/slump-chinas-home-prices-sales-set-worsen-this-year-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>经济复苏乏力，1-4月中国财政收入下降2.7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fiscal-revenue-shrank-27-jan-april-amid-shaky-economic-recovery-2024-05-20/</link><description>继1月至3月下滑2.3%后，2024年前4个月中国财政收入同比下滑2.7%，进一步表明经济复苏不平衡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fiscal-revenue-shrank-27-jan-april-amid-shaky-economic-recovery-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>面对华为的激烈竞争，苹果在中国大幅下调 iPhone 价格</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-slashes-iphone-prices-china-amid-fierce-huawei-competition-2024-05-20/</link><description>苹果公司在其中国天猫官方网站上推出了大幅折扣活动，部分 iPhone 型号最高可享受 2,300 元（318 美元）的折扣。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:22:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-slashes-iphone-prices-china-amid-fierce-huawei-competition-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>奥迪与上汽集团合作开发中国专用电动汽车平台</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/audi-partner-saic-develop-china-specific-ev-platform-2024-05-20/</link><description>大众汽车旗下高端品牌奥迪周一表示，将与其中国合资伙伴上汽集团共同开发一个新的中国专用智能电动汽车平台。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/audi-partner-saic-develop-china-specific-ev-platform-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>在反对派抗议中，尼泊尔总理赢得议会信任投票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/amid-opposition-protests-nepal-pm-wins-parliamentary-vote-confidence-2024-05-20/</link><description>尼泊尔总理周一赢得议会信任投票，反对派抗议要求议会对其内政部长在从政前非法收受多家公司资金的指控进行调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:08:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/amid-opposition-protests-nepal-pm-wins-parliamentary-vote-confidence-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>彭博社报道，中国监管机构计划召开欧洲投资者会议以重振股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulators-plan-european-investor-meet-revive-stocks-bloomberg-reports-2024-05-20/</link><description>彭博社周一援引不愿透露姓名的知情人士的话报道称，中国市场监管机构计划本周与欧洲投资者举行会议，以重振他们对全球第二大股市的兴趣。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulators-plan-european-investor-meet-revive-stocks-bloomberg-reports-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>新台湾总统就任后台中关系的关键事实</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/key-facts-taiwan-china-relations-new-taiwan-president-takes-office-2024-05-20/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德在一月份赢得选举后于周一就职。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 06:34:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/key-facts-taiwan-china-relations-new-taiwan-president-takes-office-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>独家：特斯拉采取损害控制措施，为欧洲车队买家提供折扣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-doing-damage-control-discounts-european-fleet-buyers-2024-05-20/</link><description>特斯拉正在努力安抚一些欧洲租赁公司，因为该汽车制造商一再下调零售价格，导致其车队的价值大幅下降，而且其缓慢的服务和昂贵的维修疏远了他们的企业客户。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 05:03:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-doing-damage-control-discounts-european-fleet-buyers-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾敦促中国允许对有争议的南海浅滩进行审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-should-allow-scrutiny-disputed-shoal-2024-05-20/</link><description>在指责北京破坏黄岩岛海洋环境后，菲律宾周一挑战中国开放黄岩岛接受国际监督。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 03:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-should-allow-scrutiny-disputed-shoal-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国商务部禁止部分美国企业从事进出口活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-commerce-ministry-bans-some-us-firms-import-export-activities-2024-05-20/</link><description>中国商务部周一表示，将禁止部分美国企业从事与中国相关的进出口活动，包括向台湾出售武器，并禁止它们在中国进行新的投资。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 02:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-commerce-ministry-bans-some-us-firms-import-export-activities-2024-05-20/</guid></item></channel></rss>